text: Skaneateles may refer to, in the United States: * Skaneateles (village), New York, in Onondaga County * Skaneateles (town), New York, in Onondaga County * Skaneateles Lake, one of the Finger Lakes in New York State ** Skaneateles Creek, the creek that drains the lake * Skaneateles Community, a short-lived 1840s utopian social experiment near Mottville, in the town of Skaneateles, New York
title: Skaneateles
